mod-page-background.description:
Used by `--spectrum-page-background-color`.
Defaults to `var(--spectrum-gray-75)`, if not set.

mod-page-content-tap-highlight.description:
Used by `--spectrum-page-content-tap-highlight`.
Defaults to `var(--spectrum-transparent-black-25)`, if not set.

spectrum-page-background-color.description:
Defined in `:root`.
Used by `:root`.
Defaults to `var(--mod-page-background, var(--spectrum-gray-75))`, if not set.

spectrum-page-content-tap-highlight.description:
Defined in `:root`.
Used by `:root`.
Defaults to `var(--mod-page-content-tap-highlight, var(--spectrum-transparent-black-25))`, if not set.
